This,API,allows,you,to,find,Visa,accepting,merchants,by,geolocation,and,provides,a,way,to,search,for,Merchant,Store,Locations,using,the,Merchant,Name,Category,and,geolocation,filters,such,as,Address,or,Postal,Code,Some,key,features,include,search,millions,of,merchants,across,multiple,merchant,categories,and,find,merchants,around,you,using,your,location,The,Visa,Merchant,Locator,service,helps,you,easily,locate,merchants,by,specified,category,and,location